column5: Anyone planning on being at Frog Rapids Camp first week of August, or East Side of Lac Seul? I will be up there...heading out to Lac Seul Daily. Anyone Know if the Bindo Lake Boat Launch is still Open and useable? I hate using Deception Bay....takes to long to boat to East Side. Avgerage Joe
We will be up there same week, staying at Abram Lake Park. We too, plan on launching into Lac seul a few times.
